    "For \"dialects\", we use 'dialect', 'national variety' (subword for inflections of 'variety'), 'national variation', and 'Creole'.",
    "For \"socio-cultural\", we use the words \"cultural\", and \"socio-cultural\".",
    "We restrict to the year range 2000-2023.Dialect awareness has been shown to improve the performance of NLP tasks such as machine translation [Sun et al.",
    "2023], speech recognition [Plüss et al. 2023].",
